artists.biography: Mouse Rat is the fictional rock band from NBC's comedy series 'Parks and Recreation'. Led by the loveable goodball Andy Dwyer, played by Chris Pratt who actually performs lead vocals and guitar, several full-length versions of songs from the show were released for download.
